{"tid":2050603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今年64集會，係為左打國際戰綫，幫吓佢地記起31年前發生過咩事","createTime":"2020-06-04T08:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T08:54:00.000Z","uid":47144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab5ca479830fb7776e7c234170aca0a1181f145","tid":2050603,"uid":47144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:40:57.000Z","msg":"利申咗先<br />\n我對上三年都係杯葛支聯會嘅集會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但今晚嘅意義在於喚起西方世界嘅回憶<br />\n記翻起31年前天安門廣場發生咩事<br />\n西方世界曾經匪夷所思嘅大屠殺<br />\n<br />\n現時全球反中情緒高涱 <br />\n話唔定香港人聽日又可以上國際頭條<br />\n<br />\n香港人應努力煽風點火<br />\n今晚見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8518cdd72685fe445dc4df2818a80f901bb681d5","tid":2050603,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:50:49.000Z","msg":"[思想武裝]我們不妨功利一點看待｢六四｣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2049910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2049910</a>"},{"pid":"cc83a8de9fb65c178eea7bd9820073e0d1164f22","tid":2050603,"uid":47144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}